org.alljoyn.bus

Class MarshalBusException

  • Object
    • Throwable
      • Exception
        • BusException
          • MarshalBusException
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Serializable

    public class MarshalBusException
extends BusException
    AllJoyn marshalling related exceptions. Marshalling exceptions occur when a Java type cannot be marshalled into an AllJoyn type and vice versa.

    When a Java type cannot be marshalled into an AllJoyn type, the message reported will be similar to cannot marshal class java.lang.Byte into 'a{ss}' . When an AllJoyn type cannot be marshalled into a Java type, the message reported will be similar to cannot marshal '(i)' into byte.
